source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Start a recording

Usage: bl record start [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --screenshots [<screenshots>]  Capture screenshots after each action [default: true] [possible values: true, false]
  -v, --verbose                      Enable debug logging
      --snapshots                    Capture HTML snapshots
      --sources                      Include source information
      --bidi                         Record raw BiDi commands in the recording
      --name <name>                  Name for the recording
      --title <title>                Title shown in trace viewer (defaults to name)
      --format <format>              Screenshot format: jpeg or png [default: jpeg]
      --quality <quality>            JPEG quality 0.0-1.0 (ignored for png) [default: 0.5]
      --headless                     Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json                         Output as JSON
  -h, --help                         Print help

Examples:
  bl record start
  # Start recording with screenshots (default)

  bl record start --screenshots=false
  # Record without screenshots

  bl record start --snapshots
  # Record with screenshots and HTML snapshots

  bl record start --format png
  # Use PNG format instead of JPEG (larger files, lossless)

  bl record start --quality 0.1
  # Lower JPEG quality for smaller recording files

  bl record start --title "Login Flow"
  # Set a title shown in the trace viewer
